sequenceDiagram
  participant G as Ground
  participant CRK as CRK-1
  participant CAS as CAS
  participant LLM as Cognitive Plane

  G->>CRK: Command / Payload
  CRK->>CAS: Init Span
  CRK->>CRK: Pre-run Invariants (PE + SE)
  alt violation
    CRK->>CAS: Fault + SAFE-MODE
  else pass
    CRK->>LLM: Execute (if profile permits)
    LLM-->>CRK: Result
    CRK->>CRK: Post-run Invariants
    CRK->>CAS: Receipt + Epistemic Receipt
    CRK->>G: Telemetry
  end
